==特性==
Poppler可以使用[[Cairo_(繪圖)|Cairo]]和Splash两个后端绘制PDF文档，而它的特性又取决于所使用的后端。一个基于[[Qt|Qt4]]绘制框架的第三方后端“Arthur”也是可用的，但是并不完整，而且已不再是活跃开发状态了。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mail-archive.com/poppler@lists.freedesktop.org/msg02641.html|title=Re: [poppler] Qt4 Arthur|author=Albert Astals Cid|date=15 May 2009|work=mail-archive.com|accessdate=2018-06-22|archive-date=2018-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623004821/https://www.mail-archive.com/poppler@lists.freedesktop.org/msg02641.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>  [[Glib|Glib]]，Qt3和Qt4的绑定提供了对Poppler后端的交互界面。尽管Qt3和Qt4绑定仅仅支持Splash后端，有一组可用的补丁支持使用Cairo后端的Qt4绑定。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://github.com/giddie/poppler-qt4-cairo-backend|title=giddie/poppler-qt4-cairo-backend|work=GitHub|accessdate=2018-06-22|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809031936/https://github.com/giddie/poppler-qt4-cairo-backend|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，Poppler 项目现在依然不希望将这个特性添加到 Poppler 库中。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=25240|title=Bug 25240 – Cairo backend for Qt4 wrapper|work=freedesktop.org|accessdate=2018-06-22|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622193321/https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=25240|dead-url=no}}</ref>

后端的一些特点包括：

*Cairo:矢量图形反锯齿，以及透明物件渲染。<ref name="pop-wiki" />
**Cairo并不对诸如扫描文档的位图进行平滑处理。
**Cairo并不依赖于[[X_Window|X Window]]环境，因此Poppler得以像[[Wayland|Wayland]]一样在不同平台如[[Windows|Windows]]或[[Mac_OS|Mac OS]]上运行。

*Splash:支持位图的微小滤波 。<ref name="pop-wiki" />

Poppler还有一个文字渲染后端，可以从[[命令行界面|命令行]]实用程序 pdftotext 调用。它可以用来在命令行下从 PDF 文件中搜索字符串（比如说同 <code>[[grep|grep]]</code>连用）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.linuxjournal.com/video/searching-pdf-files-grep|title=Searching PDF Files With grep|accessdate=2010-01-21|archive-date=2010-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100212233230/http://www.linuxjournal.com/video/searching-pdf-files-grep|dead-url=no}}</ref>

具体的方法示例：<syntaxhighlight lang="bash">
pdftotext file.pdf - | grep string
</syntaxhighlight>Poppler支持使用[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]，注释和表单的可交互式文档，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.linux-magazine.com/Online/News/Poppler-PDF-library-learns-Javascript/%28kategorie%29/0|title=Poppler PDF library learns Javascript|accessdate=2010-01-21|date=September 12, 2008|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622192815/http://www.linux-magazine.com/Online/News/Poppler-PDF-library-learns-Javascript/%28kategorie%29/0|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但还不支持呈现完整的XFA表单。<ref name="bug18935">{{citation |url=https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=18935 |title=Bug 18935 - Form data is not saved for PDF files using XFA forms, will show old values when opened in acroread / Adobe Reader |date=2008-12-07 |accessdate=2018-06-22 |archive-date=2018-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622193059/https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=18935 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{portalpar|自由軟體}}

